{"tid":226454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(游水)五分鐘游二百米蛙式","createTime":"2017-05-02T13:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T07:47:35.000Z","uid":104598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3a0198bca083932d14fc4c8e52ed8d297bf8ae","tid":226454,"uid":104598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:52:13.000Z","msg":"近排想考拯溺 距有個標準係要五分鐘游二百米 點樣游先快d 蛙式既話"},{"pid":"f107c85779323d5d87cc30ce22c1adef9bdf70f1","tid":226454,"uid":78175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:02:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3deb2f899a6a36ffadb30f4a670bbb87248e87a0","tid":226454,"uid":78175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9ce8a2472fefda62044fb48a5004214518e2cdd","tid":226454,"uid":104598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>近排想考拯溺 距有個標準係要五分鐘游二百米 點樣游先快d 蛙式既話</blockquote><br />\n感受水流節奏 例如對手撥完唔係即刻踢腳 Feel到水流有向前既推動先再踢腳<br />\n單單呢樣野已經可以快唔少<br />\n另外撥手個陣向兩邊用力 撥手用力要「深」唔係要快<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申游蛙式都叫幾快下 咩式都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我游水係自學既 所以自由式唔多標準 鐘意用蛙式多d"},{"pid":"7baaa033e71f87f7b0b93fdbe7f473521f5c5ecb","tid":226454,"uid":104598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:12:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有一樣野我見唔少游蛙式嘅人 都係撥手同踢腳同步做 記得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我頭先游完過咗三十幾秒 月尾就考 有無得練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979f18422e7abbec23c7be4fdace120974b609e8","tid":226454,"uid":79586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:23:09.000Z","msg":"節奏要啱 <br />\n高頭 <br />\n收腳（慢） <br />\n低頭 <br />\n蹬夾 （加速）要翻腳掌<br />\n滑行"},{"pid":"c52c0359db6c92a3c86f89aaa0765e97982b3d9d","tid":226454,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"其實唔難喎"},{"pid":"fa708e8805737aba6831d3042dd4fe45ce39f25b","tid":226454,"uid":39278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"用力游"},{"pid":"96c8df859892111af662f3d8f1329252c518376b","tid":226454,"uid":20557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有一樣野我見唔少游蛙式嘅人 都係撥手同踢腳同步做 記得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我頭先游完過咗三十幾秒 月尾就考 有無得練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入學試？ <br />\n真係考章只有1分40秒100米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493648eead7899590432e17f31d74228851b05ae","tid":226454,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"蝶式應該點游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 學過捷泳同蛙式"},{"pid":"34e5568491d09ca3c7d7fa29ce92f59676d66d2e","tid":226454,"uid":1778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"曾經考過 磁章 的揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n銅章其實好易啦"},{"pid":"b2a935b3046bffc6a347791925acfea5bc96631e","tid":226454,"uid":81884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:06:48.000Z","msg":"磁章。   只係個有顏色嘅銅章 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慢慢游一分鐘一個都得<br />\n前提系你對腳夾到水"},{"pid":"e9e79da625887849a5a39fa426dffb0c39a3401e","tid":226454,"uid":9500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有一樣野我見唔少游蛙式嘅人 都係撥手同踢腳同步做 記得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我頭先游完過咗三十幾秒 月尾就考 有無得練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入學試？ <br />\n真係考章只有1分40秒100米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考果陣邊有會咁手緊 一般都會鬆手d"},{"pid":"716fe534330c34ba18bf50507aec0d4fa0187418","tid":226454,"uid":52505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:13:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有一樣野我見唔少游蛙式嘅人 都係撥手同踢腳同步做 記得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撥手即係雙向兩邊撥定伸出去果下<br />\n如果向兩邊撥同時踢腳個姿勢咪怪到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15663b0987e647db9a5abd2d656a4e17785d872","tid":226454,"uid":81884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:55:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有一樣野我見唔少游蛙式嘅人 都係撥手同踢腳同步做 記得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我頭先游完過咗三十幾秒 月尾就考 有無得練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入學試？ <br />\n真係考章只有1分40秒100米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考果陣邊有會咁手緊 一般都會鬆手d</blockquote><br />\n其實都系睇考官。<br />\n 帶過考試 見過四分鐘出現 銅章 pass.左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n救生章 通常啲師兄練好先會去考。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc592e8dda91d0753a830e6c0d70450ec1a7fdeb","tid":226454,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇片話蛙式就入水用鼻呼，出水就口吸 捷泳就入水用口鼻同時呼，出水用口吸 咁係岩定唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8dc5fd41dc6e14638b813df285ae32d59851c0e","tid":226454,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩睇片話蛙式就入水用鼻呼，出水就口吸 捷泳就入水用口鼻同時呼，出水用口吸 咁係岩定唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0392638eb3b96bb68fdd4d95b9b3e9471de666e6","tid":226454,"uid":20557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T07:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩睇片話蛙式就入水用鼻呼，出水就口吸 捷泳就入水用口鼻同時呼，出水用口吸 咁係岩定唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n口吸 正確<br />\n有用鼻呼 正確"},{"pid":"3bc5b114cc537c2cc771465db583e9d22b237e51","tid":226454,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"5分鐘200個水試我直頭skip左因為實得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1分40有d女游2分幾都照pass"}]}